data.description: If you're looking for a home minutes from town, look no further. This home features 2 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms and is move-in ready. With the wheelchair ramp leading to the front door, you will find the bedrooms and bathrooms located on one side of the house, with an open concept kitchen and living room located on the other end of the house. The workshop garage has electric and water, and the property is fully fenced. Underground cellar/storage, a gun range, and a fenced garden area are a few of the additional features this property has ready to go.
